nodes.text: LEGO Star Wars is a line of lego sets. Lego Star Wars sets were produced in 1999 and beyond. Lego Star Wars sets were made from the original, prequel and also sequel movie trilogy. Based on the films stories of Solo: A Star Wars Story, and Rogue One: A Star Wars Story. Also on the animated series The Clone Wars, Rebels, Bad Batch, Yoda Chronicles. And there can still be animated series. And the Mandalorian too. And on the game The Old Republic. There are also many lego star wars animated series, books, games and everything else, see below. There were LEGO Star Wars battle packs in this universe. They are intended for those who want to collect a large army of clones or stormtroopers or some other soldiers.
